This project contains an API for manipulating polynomials. It allows the user to:
- represent polynomials using coefficients
- add two polynomials
- check if a certain value is a root of a polynomial

It also contains a driver that demonstrates the use of this functionality.

This project was created by me, Evan Simanovskis on 2026/5/20 for the CSCB07 course at UTSC.
